<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Photovoltaïque</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.spwd
ls
css" />
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <nav class="sidebar">
      <button class="btn active">
        <span class="icon">🧠</span>
        <span>Entretien intelligent</span>
      </button>
      <button class="btn"><span class="icon">🧹</span> Nettoyage</button>
      <button class="btn"><span class="icon">🛡️</span> Protection</button>
      <button class="btn"><span class="icon">⚡</span> Performances</button>
      <button class="btn"><span class="icon">📱</span> Applications</button>
      <button class="btn"><span class="icon">🗑️</span> Mes fichiers inutiles</button>
      <button class="btn"><span class="icon">🔍</span> Télescope</button>
      <button class="btn"><span class="icon">☁️</span> Nettoyage cloud</button>
      <button class="btn"><span class="icon">🤖</span> Assistant</button>
    </nav>

    <main class="main-content">
      <img src="your-logo-or-image.png" alt="Logo" class="main-image" />
      <h1>Heureux de vous revoir !</h1>
      <p>Pour commencer, lancez une analyse rapide et complète de votre système.</p>
      <button class="main-button">Analyser</button>
    </main>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
<styles>
  body, html {
    margin: 0; padding: 0; height: 100%;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #3a0564 0%, #6b27b9 100%);
    color: white;
  }
  
  .container {
    display: flex;
    height: 100vh;
  }
  
  .sidebar {
    width: 220px;
    background-color: #240441;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 20px 10px;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  
  .btn {
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    color: white;
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 16px;
    padding: 10px 15px;
    border-radius: 15px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.3s;
    font-weight: 500;
  
    &:hover,
    &.active {
      background: #5f1ab6;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px #b772f3;
    }
  }
  
  .main-content {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 40px;
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .main-image {
    width: 180px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px #b772f3);
  }
  
  h1 {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  
  p {
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    opacity: 0.75;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  
  .main-button {
    background: #8f2eff;
    border: none;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    padding: 20px 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    width: 140px;
    height: 140px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px #b772f3;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  
    &:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 0 40px #d199ff;
    }
  }
</styles>